name: Still Life 16.1
description:
Fizz Pop (b.1974)  
August 2021  
7250 x 5800 pixels  

  This work is a visual representation of key NFT’s minted by the end of August 2021.  The Islands & Planets minted on Foundation are represented by eleven tulips; four red tulips being unsold works.  The Still Life collection on Hic et Nunc is represented by eighteen stalks of wheat.  Flower 01, my first NFT sold of Rarible & Flower 35.0 minted on Kalamint are represented by a tulip & stalk of wheat resting at the foot of the vase.
